SSHFling Debian Source Package Draft
====================================

This directory is a packaging draft for Debian and Ubuntu review work. It is
not an upload-ready official archive package until it has been built, linted,
and reviewed through the normal Debian/Ubuntu sponsorship path.

Before upload, complete the review work recorded in
docs/official-distro-readiness.md and run the normal distro validation path:

* dpkg-buildpackage
* lintian
* autopkgtest
* WNPP/ITP and sponsor review for Debian
* Ubuntu sponsorship or sync review where applicable
